text: Mon Redee Sut Txi (born 10 February 1982) is an archer from Malaysia. Redee Sut Txi competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Mon Redee Sut TxiMon Redee SUT TXI == References == Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian archers Category:Olympians for Malaysia
